1
00:00:09,050 --> 00:00:11,930
Hey, what are you doing here all by yourself?

2
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:14,010
Kamiki-san!

3
00:00:14,010 --> 00:00:16,680
Is that a bento Mizuki made for you?

4
00:00:16,680 --> 00:00:18,230
Yeah.

5
00:00:18,230 --> 00:00:21,900
You two are so different.
He's such a reliable older brother.

6
00:00:21,900 --> 00:00:24,770
What do you mean by "different"?
Don't say it like that.

7
00:00:24,770 --> 00:00:26,650
I've been working hard too, you know.

8
00:00:26,650 --> 00:00:27,900
Alright, alright.

9
00:00:27,900 --> 00:00:29,610
You're right. You've been working hard too.

10
00:00:29,610 --> 00:00:31,200
Of course I have!

11
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:33,530
I actually closed a deal
all on my own recently.

12
00:00:33,530 --> 00:00:36,120
Oh, I heard about that.
You did a great job.

13
00:00:36,120 --> 00:00:37,120
The department manager told me.

14
00:00:37,450 --> 00:00:40,580
I've got my own ambitions too.

15
00:00:42,330 --> 00:00:43,170
Oh, by the way...

16
00:00:43,170 --> 00:00:44,340
What is it?

17
00:00:44,340 --> 00:00:47,130
I have an upcoming business trip
that's crucial to the company's future.

18
00:00:47,130 --> 00:00:48,550
Why don't you come with me?

19
00:00:48,550 --> 00:00:50,680
Really? I can go with you?

20
00:00:50,680 --> 00:00:52,470
Since you've been working so hard,
I'm making an exception for you.

21
00:00:53,680 --> 00:00:56,720
Are you sure I won't just get in the way?

22
00:00:57,350 --> 00:01:00,140
Having you there
will help keep things light.

23
00:01:00,140 --> 00:01:01,900
In fact,
would you mind coming along to keep me company?

24
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:03,810
I'd love to! I'd absolutely love to go!

25
00:01:03,810 --> 00:01:07,360
Great. I'll leave the hotel reservations
to you, then.

26
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:09,780
Yes, sir! Thank you so much.
I won't let you down!

27
00:01:09,780 --> 00:01:11,820
Good.

28
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:18,450
This... This is...
